【 360 Rotatable & Easy Installation】 360 degree rotation allows you to rotate any angle you desired, you only need adjust the expandable leg of backseat headrest mount, so it can be installed immediately.

【 Shockproof Protection】 The soft rubber lining protects your devices from friction, the telescoping arms can effectively prevent vibration while firmly grasping your rear seat and devices. Good car travel accessories for long trips.
【 More Convenient & Enjoyable】 Universal headrest iPad holder will bring you a great fun when watching movies, reading, playing games and listening to music with no hands during long car journeys.

【 Upgrade Version】 This updated version of the car headrest phone mount can be adapted to more car models. Headrest rod distance adaptation range: 2.8 - 5.9 inch( 70-150mm) .Like Truck, SUV, Sedan. ❗ Doesn't fit the car headrests without metal headrest rods, like Volvo.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy phone or tablet holder
reviews.reviewText: The Car Tablet Headrest Holder has become an absolute game-changer for our family road trips. This product has exceeded our expectations in every way, making long journeys with kids not just bearable but enjoyable.First and foremost, the installation is incredibly simple. The adjustable clamp securely attaches to the headrest, ensuring that the tablet mount stays in place even during bumpy rides. The versatility of this holder, compatible with a wide range of tablets and devices, is a huge advantage. We've used it with iPads, Galaxy Tabs, and other tablets, and it accommodates all of them effortlessly.The 360-degree rotatable ball joint allows for customized viewing angles, keeping the kids entertained and comfortable. Whether they're watching movies, playing games, or reading, the tablet remains at the perfect eye level.But what really sets this headrest holder apart is its sturdiness. It can withstand the enthusiastic tapping of little fingers and doesn't wobble or sag, even with larger tablets. The security strap is an added layer of protection, preventing accidental drops.The ability to free up our hands and keep our kids engaged during road trips has made our journeys much smoother. No more constant requests to hold the tablet, and no more distractions while driving. It's a safety and sanity saver!In conclusion, the Car Tablet Headrest Holder is a must-have road trip essential for any family. Its ease of use, compatibility, durability, and adjustable features make it an invaluable addition to our travel setup. This product has truly transformed our road trips and made them enjoyable for everyone. Highly recommended!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 11, 2024
reviews.reviewText: My family really enjoy this product. Especially my daughter who is the main person who uses it. Long car rides don't bother her anymore. It is super simple to attach, easy to adjust, and holds up great on any type of road.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Lifesaver on road trip for 1.5 year old!
reviews.reviewText: This was perfect for our 1.5 year old! She’s in a rear facing car seat and I was able to attach it to the headrest below the mirror. She can watch movies easily. We are using an old iPhone SE. It fits perfectly and I can plug in a charger while it’s in use so I never have to worry about the phone battery running out. It moves around easily to change orientation or direction but it’s sturdy so it doesn’t flop around or move unless you choose to move it. It’s very easy to set up for the first time. And taking the phone in/out is also very easy. Well made product! Highly recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 27, 2023

reviews.reviewText: When I pick up our grandchild from daycare, I put my iPhone into this holder and play CocoMelon videos for him to watch on the ride home. It works great, easy to install, and my phone is secure.

reviews.reviewText: Fabulous, as expected. Easy to install, no dramas at all for my two kids for our longer journey this holiday. My only thing is making the mistake with little Miss in her car seat, of leaning in to get something she dropped on the floor and I always take my head out with the corner of it :) So, parents beware, haha, but that's just a parent's point! The product is rock solid! Leaves a mark but doesn't hurt my iPad or mark it, just my noggin :)

I didn’t have high hopes for this product when I ordered it. I needed one to be delivered in less than 24hrs and this one was. Holds an Ipad really well, never drops down, doesn’t fall out. As long as you tighten the adjustment point enough. Worked so good a bought a second one.
